<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201119/a4f01ab45ea24872b92e70ae52ea4d1e.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">高云淡书法作品</span></img></p>
